{"id":"7aee30e5-382f-4671-aa89-b692b733ef0b","name":"Veldrin - Drow Rogue - ALT","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\">𝔸ℕ𝕐ℙ𝕆𝕍◇𝕊𝔽𝕎 𝕀ℕ𝕋ℝ𝕆<br>Alternate Scenario!<br><em>(Mean Drow X Any!User)</em><br>❄️<span style=\"color: rgb(42, 71, 168)\">◈━◈━◈━◈━◈❄️</span><br><br><strong>Eldrana has been vanquished, and Veldrin's near lifelong mission is over. Resting in the warm waters of a hotspring in the Evermelt in the frozen north, Veldrin searches for meaning, something to achieve next. </strong><br><br><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 129, 208)\"><em>My first D&amp;D series are finally getting their promised alt scenes, I'm so sorry it took so long! I'll be doing 6 of these and then new D&amp;D characters! </em></span><span style=\"color: rgb(135, 196, 255)\"><em>I really can't believe Vel hit 50k! Thank you for chatting with him even though he is rude and mean. Initally I'd had a simple like, fluffy hot spring thing planned, but this is slightly different.</em></span><br><br>❄️<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">✸</span><span style=\"color: rgb(135, 196, 255)\"><em>Alt Scenes Planned </em></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">✸❄️</span><br><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/7aee30e5-382f-4671-aa89-b692b733ef0b_character-veldrin-drow-rogue-alt\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(29, 91, 178); color: inherit\">Veldrin</mark></strong></span></a><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92)\"><strong> || </strong></span><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/43a4a69f-e4d0-48f1-8d76-8252aa6dc1e9_character-temerity-tiefling-sorcerer-alt\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(35, 58, 165); color: inherit\">Temerity</mark></strong></span></a><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92)\"><strong> || </strong></span><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characte